name: Lost in The Rhythm
description:
As you know, drummers are the guardian of the beat. He is responsible for the beat that the band played. But have you ever wonder about the drummer that playing his own solos with bass or guitar player as the keeper of the tempo?

I think I've seen one. I found him, having fun while playing music under the city of New York. The sound of the train passing by somehow intertwined with the music that they all playing. For me, I can feel the emotion, not only through his face, but also the sound, and the situation around.
